{"type": "article", "id": 31956, "title": "这些手拿包，还想为你讲一个故事｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-07T23:04:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 32546, "name": "Maven Design"}, {"id": 32547, "name": "Joogii"}, {"id": 32548, "name": "Pulpo"}, {"id": 32549, "name": "Williams Sonoma"}, {"id": 32550, "name": "BrandOpus"}, {"id": 32551, "name": "Hermann August Weizenenger"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 147, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160907225354n1ayAdNhDCGVw4X8.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Makeup by Hermann August Weizenenger</h3><p>在巴黎家居装饰博览会秋展上，德国工业设计师 <a href=\"http://www.hermannaugustweizenegger.de/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hermann August Weizenenger</a> 和德国家居品牌 <a href=\"http://www.pulpoproducts.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pulpo</a> 合作推出了一套名为 Makeup 的陶瓷花瓶。随着观察角度的变化，你会发现花瓶表面散发出不同的彩虹光泽，仔细观察还能看到一道道浅浅的横条。为了将手工玻璃的特性复制到陶瓷上，Weizenenger 特意在表面使用了一种能够反射出光线的乳白色漆料。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225657l6IBn5KM2AvUrPJG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225657JCfQR2TiXlO3VBAW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658924\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225657Ilx6FbH0jNQ5nth1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685819\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225658hmMIzoJX6T4RkLax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.237164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225658ULuARxNYiKSCTzd2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.790954\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609072256589ZWn4KvbqpuVItaL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654034\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Avocado Tool Kit by Maven Design</h3><p>美国设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.mavendesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maven Design</a> 最近为家居品牌 <a href=\"http://www.williams-sonoma.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Williams Sonoma</a> 设计了一套处理牛油果的<a href=\"http://www.mavendesign.com/ws-avocado-tools\" rel=\"nofollow\">工具</a>，涵盖了挖取、切片、碾碎以及储存这些基本功能，搭配上采用牛油果配色的手柄，看起来格外舒适清爽。你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.williams-sonoma.com/search/avocado/cooks-tools/results.html?N=4294967249&amp;words=avocado\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这四款工具，售价从 7.95 到 17.95 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225736TrzZjHfanBSbm3sV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225735d23OZxpqhR7mt1PH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225735Qn2IsCE8k5bKif3p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225735dCwFlKkZnJqmVBfr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609072257355ZSBYzqRT6WsAhuj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225736BJVWLm2NE4QuKkai.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Well Light by Stefan Nosko</h3><p>你见过能打捞出光的井吗？这款名为 Well Light 的台灯由来自斯洛伐克美术与设计学院（Academy of Fine Arts and Design）的 Stefan Nosko 以水井为灵感设计，是 <a href=\"http://ifworlddesignguide.com/entry/197024-well\" rel=\"nofollow\">2016 年 iF 学生设计奖</a>的入围作品。灯具的顶部是一个配有黄铜组件的木制辘轳，一条织线穿过横梁的小孔连接着小小的灯泡。玻璃容器的下半部分呈哑光和蓝色，要调整光线的明暗程度就需要像打捞水桶一样改变灯泡所在的位置，越往上也就越明亮。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225626BTmQnXqe8zWcCk5H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225626jMfHCKvVt4EOBoAi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225626aD6nxJTKUc78Egsz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225627d20s4kSgYlB65U8h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225626kGDpl62EwqFZ5oiH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225627HpOU0DaoSdq2FvTL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>French Touch Collection by Joogii</h3><p>美国洛杉矶的 <a href=\"http://www.joogiidesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Joogii</a> 设计工作室此前曾以法国浩室风格（French house）的音乐（如果你不清楚这是什么样的音乐，可以听一听<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/joogiidesign/french-touch-mixtape-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>中 Joogii 挑选的合集）为灵感设计了一张五彩斑斓的<a href=\"http://www.joogiidesign.com/the-french-touch-chair\" rel=\"nofollow\">彩虹椅</a>，向包括 Daft Punk 在内的一批实验音乐人致敬。最近他们在此基础上推出了一套名为 <a href=\"http://www.joogiidesign.com/french-touch-collection1\" rel=\"nofollow\">French Touch</a> 的家具，包含重新设计过的椅子、咖啡桌、边桌以及装饰品。几何造型的丙烯酸塑料板表面覆有二向色薄膜，使它们能够在光线下呈现出如同万花筒一般的色调。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225515Y5RMkXCDxK4LHfsF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225515RQFNq0AYI6O9KpUs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609072255154AvQFCaubU5cZXmB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225515tJ3Ofw2LRkBaAyU4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225515XlsAHbkB2ji37R5Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.300000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225515l2OcW0dJKe9HzyiL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Book Clutch Bag by MrsChaplinShop</h3><p>还记得那个把铁盒做成一本书的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/30482.html\">茶叶包装设计</a>吗？莫斯科 <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/MrsChaplinShop\" rel=\"nofollow\">MrsChaplinShop</a> 出品的手拿包同样是以书籍作为设计灵感。每一个手拿包都有真实的实体书作为参照，帆布外壳上那些精美的图案都由设计师 Tatiana 亲手用羊毛编织而成。除了以《小王子》、《百年孤独》和《简·爱》等经典著作为主题的款式之外，Tatiana 还允许顾客进行私人定制。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/MrsChaplinShop/items?section_id=15345030\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些吸睛的手拿包，售价从 380 到 590 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609072254445XEQCBS4iGhzpAD2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225444GdbD5fx2KaARhCcZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225444SLudJopiVGceqsZ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225444w51AQf9ClpFz2bvT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225444XHeAVSMN7uyQBaYE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225445WhZwQy2p0vqXEtAb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>J.F.Rabbit's Veg Water by BrandOpus</h3><p>由 Felix Tanzer 和 Vivid Drinks 的创始人 James Shillcock 联合创立的 <a href=\"http://www.jfrabbit.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">J.F.Rabbit's Veg Water</a> 是一个蔬菜风味的英国调味水品牌，负责品牌设计的 <a href=\"http://brandopus.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">BrandOpus</a> 为此创作了一个疯兔子博士的形象。设定中这只兔子为了制作出天然、无糖的饮料，发明出特殊的装置来提取蔬菜精华——这些画面被印在了有一小部分镂空的包装上，看起来非常有趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225409NDndgzI1ZsB6yHQ4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225408DRqz8g24ZlPyQx1W.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907225409fLQ7zpdg92YJZkDw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>"}